<msbt attribsize="8">
	<message label="999" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="999_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><20_2 arg="10" /><anim id="QuestionMark" target="actor" targetSpec="" />為什麼這種地方
<20_2 arg="9" />會有<tag a="125" b="0" arg="0x0" />啊？<pageBreak /><20_3 arg="6" /><20_3 arg="3" /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />算了，<delay8 />懂的人就是懂吧。<delay20 />這搞不好就是……
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />叫做「現代藝術」的玩意啊，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="999_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><20_2 arg="10" />那邊擺著<tag a="125" b="0" arg="0x0" />，<delay20 />
<20_2 arg="9" /><anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />總覺得令人很在意啊。<pageBreak /><20_3 arg="6" /><20_3 arg="3" /><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />對擺放這東西的傢伙來說，<delay20 />
<anim id="Laughing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />像我這樣一有時間就跑來看這東西的舉動，
一定正中那傢伙的下懷吧！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="001" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><20_2 arg="10" /><anim id="TakenAback" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><20_2 arg="9" />這蘑菇還真大顆啊！<10_4 />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="0" />等等，<delay8 /><anim id="OhGeez" target="actor" targetSpec="" />仔細一瞧，
這是<tag a="125" b="0" arg="0x0" />吧！
<20_3 arg="6" /><20_3 arg="3" /><anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我剛剛還以為是真的蘑菇咧！<delay20 />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />這家具做得還真逼真啊，<tag a="110" b="6" />。<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="002" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><20_2 arg="10" />話說<tag a="125" b="0" arg="0x0" />啊，<20_2 arg="9" /><delay8 />
雖然現在這麼大一個，<delay20 />
<20_3 arg="6" /><20_3 arg="3" /><anim id="WrySmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但要是會融化，那可就糟啦，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="003" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><20_2 arg="10" />這種地方<20_2 arg="9" />
竟然有<tag a="125" b="0" arg="0x0" /><tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />雖然不知道是誰放的，但還挺有意思啊。<20_3 arg="6" />
<20_3 arg="3" />該說是風流別緻嗎？<delay20 />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />有種簡雅的感覺啊，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="004" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><20_2 arg="10" /><tag a="125" b="0" arg="0x0" /><tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 /><20_2 arg="9" />
<anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />一看到這種積木製的家具，
我就會想起小時候啊<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><20_3 arg="6" /><20_3 arg="3" /><anim id="TakenAback" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="0" />喂！？<delay8 />你那什麼眼神啊！<delay20 />
<anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />別看我現在這個樣子，<delay8 />
我還是個小鬼的時候可愛得很咧！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="005" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><20_2 arg="10" /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="125" b="0" arg="0x0" /><tag a="110" b="0" /><20_2 arg="9" /><delay20 />
你不覺得還挺有韻味嗎？<pageBreak /><20_3 arg="6" /><20_3 arg="3" /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />這上頭的每一道傷痕<delay20 />
都代表著許多回憶啊，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="006" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我還是學生的時候啊，<delay20 />
都把讀書拋在腦後，老是顧著玩樂。<pageBreak /><20_2 arg="10" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />所以在我的眼中，<delay20 />
<20_2 arg="9" /><tag a="125" b="0" arg="0x0" />
<20_3 arg="6" /><20_3 arg="3" /><anim id="Scheming" target="actor" targetSpec="" />就只是個惡作劇用的道具啊，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="007" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><20_2 arg="10" /><20_2 arg="9" />雖然不知道是誰擺在這的，<delay20 />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但<tag a="125" b="0" arg="0x0" />
讓這裡有種很適合度假的感覺啊！
<20_3 arg="6" /><20_3 arg="3" /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />這裡能夠讓大家好好放鬆，<delay20 />
搞不好會變成<tag a="110" b="33" />的
<anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />知名景點啊，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="008" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><20_2 arg="10" /><tag a="125" b="0" arg="0x0" />
<20_2 arg="9" />會擺在這的意思是……<delay20 />
<anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />難道這裡是什麼公司嗎？
<20_3 arg="6" /><20_3 arg="3" /><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />在這種荒郊野外，<delay8 />
到底要做什麼工作啊？<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Negative" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我完全想不到咧，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="009" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><20_2 arg="10" /><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />話說，<tag a="125" b="0" arg="0x0" /><delay8 />
<20_2 arg="9" />活用了圓木本身的特色，
你不覺得給人一種有溫度的感覺嗎？<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><20_3 arg="6" /><20_3 arg="3" />像這種用自然素材做出來的家具，<delay20 />
<anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我還挺喜歡的咧，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="010" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><20_2 arg="10" /><tag a="125" b="0" arg="0x0" />啊<tag a="110" b="0" /><20_2 arg="9" />
要我看看是沒差啦，<delay20 />
<20_3 arg="6" /><20_3 arg="3" /><anim id="OhGeez" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但這風格跟我實在不搭啊，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="011" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><20_2 arg="10" /><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />感覺<tag a="125" b="0" arg="0x0" />
<20_2 arg="9" />會散發出<delay8 />吸引蟲子的香味啊。<pageBreak /><20_3 arg="6" /><20_3 arg="3" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不過，<delay8 /><anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我倒是比蟲子
更早被吸引過來啦。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Laughing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />哇～哈哈！</message>
	<message label="012" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />這一帶布置得挺不錯啊！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />感覺就像是早期電影的場景一樣。<delay20 />
<anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />啊～！<delay20 />我開始想喝可樂啦～！
<20_2 arg="10" /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />尤其是<20_2 arg="9" /><tag a="125" b="0" arg="0x0" />，<delay8 />
我覺得它營造了很棒的氣氛啊，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="013" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><20_2 arg="10" />話說<tag a="125" b="0" arg="0x0" />，<20_2 arg="9" /><delay20 />
<anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />跟我還是個小鬼時玩的玩具挺像的嘛。<pageBreak /><20_3 arg="6" /><20_3 arg="3" /><anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不管到了幾歲，<delay8 />
只要看到這種玩具，我都會很雀躍，<delay20 />
<anim id="Laughing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />看來我也是童心未泯啊，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="014" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><20_2 arg="10" />我曾經在我們島上的沙灘<delay8 />
<20_2 arg="9" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />看過用來製作
<tag a="125" b="0" arg="0x0" />的貝殼喔。
<20_3 arg="6" /><20_3 arg="3" /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />那麼小的貝殼<delay8 />
竟然能變成這麼時髦的家具，<delay20 />
<anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />ＤＩＹ還真厲害啊！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="015" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="125" b="0" arg="0x0" />啊，<delay20 />
看起來就很堅固，<delay8 />感覺特別耐用。<pageBreak /><20_2 arg="10" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />就算像這樣<20_2 arg="9" />放在戶外，
稍微受點風吹雨打，<delay20 />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />一樣堅若磐石咧，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="017" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><20_2 arg="10" /><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />只要看到<tag a="125" b="0" arg="0x0" /><20_2 arg="9" />，<delay20 />
就可以隨時感受到復活節的氣氛，<delay8 />
真開心啊。<pageBreak /><20_3 arg="6" /><20_3 arg="3" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不過，我同時<delay8 /><anim id="Laughing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />也會想起
那隻吵鬧的黃色兔子<delay20 />就是了，<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="018" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><20_2 arg="10" /><20_2 arg="9" />這不是<tag a="125" b="0" arg="0x0" />嗎？<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />說起來，<delay8 />在我小時候，<delay20 />
我老媽也常常做這些東西喔。<pageBreak /><20_3 arg="6" /><20_3 arg="3" /><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />或許她現在也繼續做著這些東西<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay frames="40" />
<anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我還是偶爾打通電話回家吧，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="019" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><20_2 arg="10" /><20_2 arg="9" /><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />說到<tag a="125" b="0" arg="0x0" />，<delay20 />
<anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />就會讓人聯想到宇宙的奇妙之處啊～<delay frames="50" />
<20_3 arg="6" /><20_3 arg="3" /><anim id="Aha" target="actor" targetSpec="" />對了，<delay20 />你相信外星人的存在嗎！？<pageBreak /><anim id="SmugFace" target="actor" targetSpec="" />其實我小時候，<delay frames="40" />曾經見過外星人喔<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Shocked" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><delay20 />騙、<delay8 />騙你的啦～<delay frames="50" /><anim id="Confused" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我是開玩笑的！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="020" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><20_2 arg="10" /><20_2 arg="9" /><anim id="Shocked" target="actor" targetSpec="" />既然外面裝飾著
<tag a="125" b="0" arg="0x0" />，<delay20 />
<anim id="QuestionMark" target="actor" targetSpec="" />該不會是有人要舉行婚禮了吧！？<pageBreak /><20_3 arg="6" /><20_3 arg="3" /><anim id="HappyFlower" target="actor" targetSpec="" />喂喂，<delay8 />真是可喜可賀啊～<delay frames="70" />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />沒想到居然有人會選擇在這舉行婚禮，<delay20 />
<anim id="SmugFace" target="actor" targetSpec="" />身為島上的居民，我感到很自豪啊，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="021" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><20_2 arg="10" /><20_2 arg="9" />把<tag a="125" b="0" arg="0x0" /><delay40 />
<anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />放在外面，<delay8 />看起來就好像<delay20 />
是從海裡打撈上來的東西。<pageBreak /><20_3 arg="6" /><20_3 arg="3" /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我還以為<delay8 />是誰把沉船裡的寶藏<delay20 />
<anim id="Laughing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />帶回來了！<tag a="110" b="6" />。
</message>
	<message label="022" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><20_2 arg="10" /><20_2 arg="9" /><anim id="Negative" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不知道是誰<delay frames="30" />
把坐鎮在夜空中的星座裝飾在地上，<delay20 />
<20_3 arg="6" /><20_3 arg="3" /><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />還挺有趣的，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="023" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><20_2 arg="10" /><20_2 arg="9" /><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />看到<tag a="125" b="0" arg="0x0" />
放在這，<delay40 /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />它的經歷就好像浮現在眼前。<pageBreak /><20_3 arg="3" /><anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />它跨越了<delay20 />無數海域環遊世界，
而旅途終點<delay8 />就是這座島<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
<20_3 arg="6" /><anim id="Laughing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />會讓人忍不住這麼想像喔！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="024" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><20_2 arg="10" /><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你看到<tag a="125" b="0" arg="0x0" />，
<20_2 arg="9" />有什麼特別的感覺嗎？<pageBreak /><20_3 arg="6" /><20_3 arg="3" /><anim id="Negative" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我一看到這個，<delay20 />就感到有些傷感。<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="OhGeez" target="actor" targetSpec="" />大概是因為上了年紀吧，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="025" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><20_2 arg="10" /><20_2 arg="9" />看到<tag a="125" b="0" arg="0x0" />後，<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我的腦中就浮現出<delay20 />燉煮好的南瓜。<pageBreak /><20_3 arg="6" /><20_3 arg="3" /><anim id="Pardon" target="actor" targetSpec="" />現在<delay20 />你的腦中是不是也<delay20 />
<anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />充滿了<delay8 />燉煮好的南瓜啊？<delay40 />
<anim id="Laughing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />哇～哈哈！</message>
	<message label="026" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><20_2 arg="10" /><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="3" />，<delay8 />你快看啊。<20_2 arg="9" /><delay frames="40" />
是<tag a="125" b="0" arg="0x0" />喔。<pageBreak /><20_3 arg="6" /><20_3 arg="3" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />只要看到這個，<delay20 /><anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />就會想起
兒時那個<delay8 />玩上一整天玩具<delay20 />
也不會覺得膩的自己啊，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="027" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><20_2 arg="10" /><20_2 arg="9" /><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />裝飾在那邊的<delay8 />
<tag a="125" b="0" arg="0x0" />，<delay20 />
感覺還挺不錯的吧。<pageBreak /><20_3 arg="6" /><20_3 arg="3" /><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我很難用言語表達清楚，<delay20 />
只要看著那個，<delay20 />就有種<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />很溫暖的感覺喔！<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
</msbt>